          "type": "verse",
          "html": "That is th꜓e nature o꜕f a꜕ll Bu꜕ddhas."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "group",
      "lang": "pi",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "html": "Tasmā h꜕i atta-kāmena"
        },
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "html": "mahattam-abhika꜓ṅkh꜕atā"
        },
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "html": "Sa꜕ddhammo ga꜕ru꜓-kāta꜕bbo"
        },
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "html": "s꜕araṃ buddhāna sā꜓sa꜕naṃ"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "group",
      "lang": "en",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "html": "Therefore de꜓siring on꜕e’s ow꜕n welfare,"
        },
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "html": "Pursui꜓ng greatest a꜕spi꜕ra꜕tions,"
        },
