          "type": "verse",
          "html": "One should reve꜕re th꜕e Tr꜕ue Dha꜕mma —"
        },
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "html": "Reco꜓llecting th꜕e Bu꜕ddha꜕’s te꜕aching."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "group",
      "lang": "pi",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "html": "Na h꜕i dhammo a꜕dhammo ca"
        },
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "html": "ubho s꜕ama-vipāki꜓no"
        },
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "html": "A꜕dhammo nirayaṃ neti"
        },
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "html": "dh꜕ammo pāpeti꜕ su꜕gga꜕tiṃ"
        }
