    },
    {
      "type": "group",
      "lang": "en",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "html": "What is true Dhamma an꜕d wh꜕at not"
        },
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "html": "Will never have the sa꜓me re꜕sults,"
        },
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "html": "While lack of Dha꜕mma꜕ le꜕ads t꜕o he꜕ll-realms —"
        },
