    },
    {
      "type": "group",
      "lang": "en",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "html": "The Dhamma guards who li꜕ves i꜕n li꜓ne wi꜕th it"
        },
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "html": "And leads to ha꜕ppi꜕ne꜕ss whe꜕n pra꜕cti꜕sed well —"
        },
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "html": "This is th꜓e blessing of we꜕ll-pr꜕acti꜕sed Dha꜕mma."
        }
      ]
    }
